#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:4
msgid "Periodic Thread Monitoring API"
msgstr "周期性线程监控 API"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:6
msgid ""
"This document describes the Periodic Thread Monitoring API feature "
"introduced in LMCache."
msgstr "本文描述了在 LMCache 中引入的周期性线程监控 API 功能。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:10
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:12
msgid ""
"The Periodic Thread Monitoring API provides HTTP endpoints to monitor and"
" inspect the status of all periodic background threads running in the "
"LMCache system. This is useful for debugging, health checking, and "
"operational monitoring."
msgstr "周期性线程监控 API 提供 HTTP 端点，以监控和检查在 LMCache 系统中运行的所有周期性后台线程的状态。这对于调试、健康检查和操作监控非常有用。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:18
msgid "API Endpoints"
msgstr "API 端点"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:20
msgid "Three API endpoints are available under the internal API server:"
msgstr "在内部 API 服务器下提供三个 API 端点："

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:23
msgid "GET /periodic-threads"
msgstr "GET /periodic-threads"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:25
msgid "Returns information about all registered periodic threads."
msgstr "返回所有注册的周期线程的信息。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:27
msgid "**Query Parameters:**"
msgstr "**查询参数：**"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:33
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "参数"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:34
msgid "Default"
msgstr "默认"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:35
#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:121
msgid "Description"
msgstr "描述"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:36
msgid "``level``"
msgstr "``level``"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:37
msgid "(none)"
msgstr "（无）"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:38
msgid "Filter by thread level (``critical``, ``high``, ``medium``, ``low``)"
msgstr "按线程级别过滤（``critical``, ``high``, ``medium``, ``low``）"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:39
msgid "``running_only``"
msgstr "``running_only``"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:40
#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:43
msgid "``false``"
msgstr "``false``"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:41
msgid "Only show running threads"
msgstr "仅显示正在运行的线程"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:42
msgid "``active_only``"
msgstr "``active_only``"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:44
msgid "Only show active threads"
msgstr "仅显示活动线程"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:46
#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:79
#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:101
msgid "**Response Example:**"
msgstr "**响应示例：**"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:75
#, python-brace-format
msgid "GET /periodic-threads/{thread_name}"
msgstr "GET /periodic-threads/{thread_name}"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:77
msgid "Returns detailed information about a specific periodic thread."
msgstr "返回有关特定周期线程的详细信息。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:96
msgid "GET /periodic-threads-health"
msgstr "GET /periodic-threads-health"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:98
msgid ""
"Quick health check for periodic threads. Returns whether all critical and"
" high-level threads are active."
msgstr "对周期性线程的快速健康检查。返回所有关键和高级线程是否处于活动状态。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:112
msgid "Thread Levels"
msgstr "线程级别"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:114
msgid "Periodic threads are categorized by importance level:"
msgstr "周期性线程按重要性级别分类："

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:120
msgid "Level"
msgstr "级别"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:122
msgid "``critical``"
msgstr "``critical``"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:123
msgid "Essential for system operation"
msgstr "系统运行所必需"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:124
msgid "``high``"
msgstr "``high``"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:125
msgid "Important for performance"
msgstr "对性能很重要"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:126
msgid "``medium``"
msgstr "``medium``"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:127
msgid "Standard background tasks"
msgstr "标准后台任务"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:128
msgid "``low``"
msgstr "``low``"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:129
msgid "Optional/auxiliary tasks"
msgstr "可选/辅助任务"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:131
msgid ""
"The health check endpoint specifically monitors ``critical`` and ``high``"
" level threads to determine system health."
msgstr "健康检查端点专门监控 ``critical`` 和 ``high`` 级别的线程以确定系统健康状况。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:135
msgid "IrrecoverableException Handling"
msgstr "不可恢复异常处理"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:137
msgid ""
"Periodic threads now properly handle ``IrrecoverableException``. When "
"such an exception is raised during thread execution:"
msgstr "周期性线程现在正确处理 ``IrrecoverableException``。当在线程执行期间引发此类异常时："

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:140
msgid "The exception is logged with full traceback"
msgstr "该异常的完整回溯将被记录。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:141
msgid "The thread run is marked as failed"
msgstr "线程运行被标记为失败"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:142
msgid "The thread **stops its execution loop** instead of continuing"
msgstr "线程 **停止其执行循环** 而不是继续执行。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:144
msgid ""
"This prevents threads from endlessly retrying operations that cannot "
"succeed."
msgstr "这可以防止线程无休止地重试无法成功的操作。"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:147
msgid "Usage Examples"
msgstr "使用示例"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:150
msgid "Check Overall Thread Health"
msgstr "检查整体线程健康状况"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:157
msgid "List All Running Threads"
msgstr "列出所有正在运行的线程"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:164
msgid "Get Critical Threads Only"
msgstr "仅获取关键线程"

#: ../../source/production/observability/periodic_thread_api.rst:171
msgid "Check Specific Thread Status"
msgstr "检查特定线程状态"


